title: VA Psychedelic Oldies - Superman (Dutch Treat ^A142 VBR)
description:
Oldies? Some stay young a long time. Unfortunately, the songs are better than they (should) sound. Pity. Anyway I am glad with Joan of Arc (A141) and Superman (A142). Quite different, good songs... Enjoy,
